{"tid":559584,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［勵志］中三學歷 30歲上車了","createTime":"2018-02-13T09:53:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T10:31:38.000Z","uid":112303,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"31bbe5ca5a6d5e26727507a2e23dc47d079fb96e","tid":559584,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T09:53:11.000Z","msg":"小弟做公屋<br />\n15歲做m記<br />\n一個月翻25日 <br />\n唔洗俾家月 零洗費<br />\n20歲已經儲左45萬同埋係經理了<br />\n之後開始俾3000家用一個月<br />\n食屋企住屋企 25歲已經儲到100萬<br />\n升左店長了 月薪20000<br />\n俾7千家用 2000娛樂<br />\n每月儲11000 儲到30歲<br />\n總資金160萬 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住去澳門all in 推咗3口細<br />\n中哂 千三萬 買左2層樓收租了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60cdd2e7e0b98319a2c7aa32bd691507dc368d1d","tid":559584,"uid":33886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T09:55:29.000Z","msg":"read"},{"pid":"eb0492f83176e2c1c4c45c58338dec5312194fed","tid":559584,"uid":116530,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T09:57:11.000Z","msg":"FF完繼續返工啦"},{"pid":"9bd120363ebba46164d070bfde1a262de27d3885","tid":559584,"uid":126519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T10:09:43.000Z","msg":"得1千2百8十期炸wo 差小小"},{"pid":"dbe7a3eeab962896e030d924c65aca90ade521e4","tid":559584,"uid":126519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T10:09:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得1千2百8十萬炸wo 差小小</blockquote>"},{"pid":"664e60a5de69768f46ca6c588d2b4cf92d21de00","tid":559584,"uid":33121,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T10:14:56.000Z","msg":"幻想完就繼續炸暑條啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"